@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>Your privacy is important to us. This page explains what information <strong>EEVEE PC SCRAPER</strong> collects and how it is used.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Product URLs:</strong> The app downloads publicly available product URLs from the Pokémon Center sitemap. This data is used to track changes in products over time.</li>
        <li><strong>Change History:</strong> The app records which products were added or removed in JSON files. No personal information is collected.</li>
        <li><strong>Discord Notifications:</strong> The app sends product change summaries to a Discord webhook. Only URLs of products are sent; no personal data is transmitted.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use This Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>To track additions and removals of products at Pokémon Center.</li>
        <li>To notify you via Discord about changes in the product catalog.</li>
        <li>To maintain a local history of product changes for reference.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>
        We do not share your personal information with third parties. Only product information is shared to the Discord webhook you configure.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
    <p>
        This application does not use cookies or other tracking technologies.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
        If you have any questions about this privacy policy, you can contact the developer at <strong>eevee-pc-scraper@example.com</strong>.
    </p>
</div>